    <headline>Polar low, yellow level, Storegga, Froeyabank, Haltenbank and Area from Storegga-Haltenbank to Greenwich meridian, 13 January 05:00 UTC to 13 January 22:00 UTC.</headline>
    <description>One or more polar lows are expected to develop Sunday morning in C3 and C4, and will during sunday move west, later south and hit the area Storegga to Haltenbanken late Sunday evening. Expect occsionally northwest gale or storm west of low center. </description>
